trans-unit.source: Defines a method for adding the <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> part of XML Paper Specification (XPS) to an XPS package.
trans-unit.target: XPS(XML Paper Specification)의 <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> 파트를 XPS 패키지에 추가하기 위한 메서드를 정의합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the `DocumentStructure` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 자세한 내용은 `DocumentStructure` 의 요소는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] 9 장을 참조, 패키지는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] 사양에서 얻을 수 있는 [XPS: 사양 및 라이선스 다운로드](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx)합니다.

trans-unit.source: Adds the <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> part of [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] to an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package.
An <see cref="T:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsStructure" /> that represents the <see langword="DocumentStructure" /> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package.

For more information about the `DocumentStructure` element of an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] package, see chapter 9 of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 자세한 내용은 `DocumentStructure` 의 요소는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xps-md.md)] , 패키지의 9 장을 참조는 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] 사양에서 얻을 수 있는 [XPS: 사양 및 라이선스 다운로드](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx)합니다.
